title: Deadtime Stories Nickelodeon HDTV

Deadtime Stories 2013, Complete Series Ten Episodes


Nickelodeon Presents: Deadtime Stories 10 Episodes

Brave-hearts listen up! If you're in the mood for something creepy, then Nickelodeon's got a Deadtime story for you.
Your soon to be favorite babysitter is the master storyteller in this brand new series,
where nightly tales are guaranteed to give you the chills. Adventure is the name of the game here,
but you'll need your wits to master the suspense. You're in for some thrilling nighttime action, so make sure you don't skip a (heart)beat.

The series stars Jennifer Stone as "The Babysitter" who reads the Deadtime Stories to the children
